title: Chicken and Broccoli Tot Kabobs
directions: Cook Green Giant Broccoli Veggie Tots and chicken nuggets according package directions.
Alternately thread Green Giant Broccoli Veggie Tots™, chicken nuggets, grape tomatoes, and string cheese onto skewers.
Serve with hot pasta sauce for dipping.
ingredients: 1 (16 ounce) package Green Giant™ Broccoli Veggie Tots
7 sticks string cheese, each cut into 3 pieces
